        {
            "title": "特朗普稱華納兄弟相關交易應該包含出售CNN",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"來源： 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/r6Ka2BbWN8.8EdthBxaHSQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/335beffa0b8b8df3f96da6c8d5ef73d3\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">來源： 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 美國總統<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:特朗普;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/特朗普\">特朗普</a>暗示，他將反對<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:華納兄弟;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/華納兄弟\">華納兄弟</a>探索任何不包括CNN新所有權內容的交易，這預示著網飛公司的收購計畫可能出現變數。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">特朗普周三在白宮與商界領導人會面時表示，「我認為任何交易都應該保證並確定CNN是交易的一部分，或者單獨出售。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我不認為現在掌管那家公司和CNN的那些人應該繼續留任，他們是一群非常不誠實的人。我認為CNN應該和其他所有業務一起被出售，」他補充道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">特朗普表示，他最擔心的是，CNN目前的管理層可能會得到回報，通過出售交易獲得的錢來繼續運營。目前，網飛和派拉蒙天舞都在競購華納兄弟。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-91c47093-0e1a-33c0-ac77-cb4cf1e36802-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">網飛已同意收購華納兄弟電視和電影公司及其HBO業務，交易估值為每股27.75美元。華納兄弟計畫在完成與網飛的交易之前，剝離其包括CNN在內的有線電視頻道。分拆計畫預計將於明年第三季度進行，華納兄弟財務長Gunnar Wiedenfels將負責後續事宜。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">派拉蒙正試圖以每股30美元全盤收購華納兄弟，包括CNN等有線電視網絡。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">荷里活和華盛頓一直在密切關注特朗普對潛在交易的評論。派拉蒙天舞執行長大衛·埃裡森的父親拉裡·埃裡森是特朗普的支持者。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">《華爾街日報》報導稱，大衛·埃裡森向特朗普承諾，如果他掌控CNN的母公司，將對這家長期以來飽受特朗普詬病的電視台進行全面改革。特朗普的女婿也參與了為埃裡森的競購方案提供的融資支持。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">埃裡森周三在致華納兄弟投資人的一封信中表示，他的方案更具價值，也更有可能通過監管審查。他敦促投資者支持他對華納兄弟的股票收購要約。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普還與網飛的聯席執行長Ted Sarandos會面，特朗普沒有公開明確表態支持任何一方。周三，他回避了有關庫什納是否參與其中的問題，但暗示他最終可能會考慮監管評估結果。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我可能會參與，也許會參與決策。這要看情況，」特朗普說。「有一些不錯的公司在競標。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump Says Warner Bros. Deal Should Include Sale of CNN (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E7%A8%B1%E8%8F%AF%E7%B4%8D%E5%85%84%E5%BC%9F%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%87%89%E8%A9%B2%E5%8C%85%E5%90%AB%E5%87%BA%E5%94%AEcnn-022147068.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-11 12:20:55",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "澳洲就業人數意外下降 澳元與澳債殖利率齊跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 澳洲就業人數意外下降，求職者減少，表明勞動力市場正在逐步放鬆，可能會使澳洲央行進一步拉長按兵不動的時間。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澳洲統計局周四公佈的數據顯示，就業人數下降21300人，其中全職崗位減少較多，而此前預期為增加20,000人。11月失業率維持在4.3%，低於經濟學家此前預測的4.4%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對政策敏感的3年期國債殖利率延續跌勢，料創下5月份以來的最大單日跌幅。澳元下跌，而股市擴大漲勢。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/A9hgIfjNWiu49W_1mkWu_A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/8054874aa3a0ebb662b405809e91db7e\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澳洲央行肩負著維持穩定低通膨和充分就業的雙重使命，使得眼下的形勢異常微妙。政策制定者正試圖在不引發廣泛失業的情況下，緩解持續的價格壓力，經濟中有限的閑置產能使這一平衡變得複雜。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c6aeef7b-92a9-3574-8b04-b4fb07ee7902-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這種局面暫時迫使澳洲央行在今年三次降息之後保持觀望，成為發達經濟體中寬鬆周期最短的國家之一。該行本周再次維持利率不變，行長Michele Bullock警告利率下一步很可能是上行。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Australian Economy Sheds Jobs, Backing RBA’s Cautious Stance</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9E%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96%E4%B8%8B%E9%99%8D-%E6%BE%B3%E5%85%83%E8%88%87%E6%BE%B3%E5%82%B5%E6%AE%96%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E9%BD%8A%E8%B7%8C-004847244.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-11 13:00:56",
